WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.270 --> 00:00:02.760
With all of the sensors available it can be tempting

00:00:02.760 --> 00:00:05.500
to use all of them, all the time. This can be

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:09.890
a bad idea. Geolocation in particular can be power hungry, so

00:00:09.890 --> 00:00:12.520
if you use it constantly you may drain the user's battery.

